name: Wikluh Sky
description:
'''Đorđe Miljenović''' ({{lang-sr-Cyrl|Ђорђе Миљеновић}}; born 10 December 1980) better known by his stage name '''Wikluh Sky''' ({{langx|sr|Виклер Скаj}}, {{lang|sr-Latn|Vikler Skaj}}) is a Serbian musician, rapper, singer, DJ, and producer.

Best known for being a member of [[Bad Copy]] hip-hop trio, he is also a part of [[Marčelo]]'s accompanying [[Shock Orchestra|Filter Crew]], and [[ragga]]muffin group/project [[Shappa]]. In addition to participating in all of the above groups and projects, Wikluh Sky maintains a solo career as well.
